th, so spread peace between yourselves.\u201d Source: al-Adab al-Mufrad lil-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 989 Grade:\u00a0Sahih\u00a0(authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0633\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":39739,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/04\/17\/salaam-reach-prophet\/","url_meta":{"origin":32215,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Our greetings of peace reach the Prophet","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 17, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, Allah has angels who journey through the earth to convey to me the greetings of peace from my nation.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 1282 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0645\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0639\u064f\u0648\u062f\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15409,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/28\/allah-teaches-adam-salaam\/","url_meta":{"origin":32215,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Salaam: Allah teaches Adam greeting of peace","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 28, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah created Adam in His image, sixty cubits tall. When He created him, Allah said: Go and greet these groups of assembled angels with peace and listen to how they greet you, for this will be the greeting\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24108,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/12\/03\/spread-salaam-be-brothers\/","url_meta":{"origin":32215,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Virtues: Spread peace, be brothers as Allah commanded","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 3, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSpread peace, feed the hungry, and be brothers as Allah Almighty has commanded you.\u201d Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 3252 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e \u0639\u064f\u0645\u064e\u0631\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33688,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/10\/03\/ibrahim-greetings-malaikah\/","url_meta":{"origin":32215,"position":4},"title":"Ibrahim on Greetings: Say as-Salaamu \u2018Alaykum for the angels too","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-A\u2019mash reported: Ibrahim al-Nakha\u2019i, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cIf you greet a single person with peace, then say: Peace be upon you all. Verily, the angels are with him.\u201d Source: Tafsi\u0304r al-Qurt\u0323ubi\u0304 4:86 \u0639\u0646 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0623\u064e\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0634 \u0639\u0646 \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0625\u0650\u0628\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0627\u0647\u0650\u064a\u0645\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u062e\u064e\u0639\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0631\u062d\u0645\u0647 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0630\u064e\u0627 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u0652\u062a\u064e \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0648\u064e\u0627\u062d\u0650\u062f\u0650 \u0641\u064e\u0642\u064f\u0644\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24815,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/11\/spread-salaam-haya-akhlaq\/","url_meta":{"origin":32215,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Akhlaq: Spread peace, offer food, be modest before Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019adh ibn Jabal reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, sent him to a people and he said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, instruct me.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSpread peace, offer food, and be modest before Allah as you would for a man of dignity from your family. If\u2026","rel":"","conte